  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package declares signatureAlg ed25519 and carries a valid sha256 hash but intentionally omits the signature value, representing a partially-signed artifact that triggers W-SI-01 (missing digital signature — structural integrity unverifiable).",
