      "acceptanceCriteria": "The power-law hemolysis damage model must be evaluated for applicability to the VAD operating regime; alternative model forms must be considered and model-form uncertainty quantified.",
      "rationale": "The Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law model is used without evaluation of alternative hemolysis model forms. Model-form uncertainty is not quantified. This represents a critical epistemic gap at MRL 5; achieved level 1 against required level 5."
    },
