    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factor gaps identified at MRL 5, the assessment team accepted the package for submission to the regulatory dossier under the condition that outstanding epistemic gaps are resolved prior to final device submission. Monte Carlo UQ results demonstrate hemolysis predictions remain below the clinical threshold across the sampled operating space, providing sufficient confidence for the current development phase decision gate. All 13 credibility factors have been formally evaluated; 7 factors were assessed with achieved levels below required levels, and 6 factors were flagged as not-assessed epistemic gaps. This package is structurally complete under the Minimal profile but carries no cryptographic signature, as the signing ceremony is deferred pending resolution of the model-form uncertainty gap.",
